India’s Potash Imports May Drop 30-35% in 2011-12

-- B y   P r a t i k   P a r i j a
-- 
2011-12-01T06:02:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-30/india-s-potash-imports-may-drop-30-35-on-high-prices-in-2010-11.html
(Corrects time period in headline in story published Nov.
30.)  India ’s imports of potash may
decline by 30 percent to 35 percent in the current financial
year on account of high prices, U.S. Awasthi, managing director
of the Indian Farmers Fertiliser Cooperative Ltd., said by
telephone today from Dubai.  To contact the reporter on this story:
